sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Caller (F015/F017)
    participant E as AuditEmitter
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant OT as OTel Exporter

    C->>E: emit(event, decision, payload)
    E-->>C: returns immediately
    E->>E: create_task(_do_emit)
    E->>E: create_task(_write_db)
    E->>E: create_task(_emit_span)
    E->>DB: INSERT audit_log entry
    E->>OT: export span attributes
    alt DB fails
        E-->>E: log NRVQ-AUD-6004
    end
    alt span fails
        E-->>E: log NRVQ-AUD-6006
    end
    C->>E: close()
    E->>E: gather pending tasks
